<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 15:14:21 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美日韩财长召开首次三边会议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us-japan-korea-finance-leaders-launch-first-trilateral-meeting-2024-04-17/</link><description>美国、日本和韩国周三召开了首次三边金融领导人会议，强调了他们对抗中国在全球贸易和供应链中日益增长的影响力的决心。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 14:49:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us-japan-korea-finance-leaders-launch-first-trilateral-meeting-2024-04-17/</guid></item><item><title>峰会报告作者表示，欧盟面临与竞争对手竞争的最后机会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/eu-faces-last-chance-compete-with-rivals-says-summit-report-author-2024-04-17/</link><description>周三，一份备受期待的欧盟领导人报告的作者表示，欧盟面临着最后的机会，可以采取必要的措施，使其能够与美国、中国和其他竞争对手进行有效竞争。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 14:00:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/eu-faces-last-chance-compete-with-rivals-says-summit-report-author-2024-04-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国球迷希望周能在主场首秀中摆脱糟糕的状态</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/formula1/chinese-fans-hope-zhou-can-shrug-off-poor-form-home-debut-2024-04-17/</link><description>周冠宇的中国车迷希望中国第一位也是唯一一位一级方程式赛车手能够摆脱糟糕的表现，在主场首秀中大放异彩，以回应那些认为他的护照是他开车的主要原因的批评者。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 13:51:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/formula1/chinese-fans-hope-zhou-can-shrug-off-poor-form-home-debut-2024-04-17/</guid></item><item><title>国际货币基金组织呼吁在选举次数最多的一年实行财政紧缩</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/imf-calls-fiscal-restraint-year-with-most-elections-ever-2024-04-17/</link><description>国际货币基金组织周三敦促各国控制财政支出并重建缓冲，但表示在全球有史以来规模最大的选举年，这可能会很困难。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 13:07:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/imf-calls-fiscal-restraint-year-with-most-elections-ever-2024-04-17/</guid></item><item><title>德中签署汽车数据共享联合声明</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/germany-china-sign-joint-declaration-car-data-sharing-2024-04-17/</link><description>德国和中国签署了一项在自动驾驶和互联驾驶方面进行合作的联合声明，德国希望这将使汽车制造商能够将数据从中国传输到德国，这对于在华外国企业来说是一个有争议的话题。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 12:43:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/germany-china-sign-joint-declaration-car-data-sharing-2024-04-17/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟商会主席警告称，中国和欧盟的贸易紧张局势可能引发全面贸易战</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/china-eu-trade-tensions-risk-full-trade-war-european-chamber-president-warns-2024-04-17/</link><description>欧洲商业游说团体负责人周三警告说，在德国总理向北京表达欧洲担忧的第二天，随着保护主义浪潮的高涨，中国和欧洲面临“慢动作火车事故”，有可能演变成一场全面的贸易战。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 11:54:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/china-eu-trade-tensions-risk-full-trade-war-european-chamber-president-warns-2024-04-17/</guid></item><item><title>白宫称对中国金属征收新关税不会影响通胀</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/new-tariffs-chinese-metals-wont-impact-inflation-white-house-says-2024-04-17/</link><description>白宫经济顾问贾里德·伯恩斯坦周三表示，拜登政府正在考虑对中国金属产品大幅提高关税，这不会影响美国的通胀，而且对于国家安全来说是必要的。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 11:47:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/new-tariffs-chinese-metals-wont-impact-inflation-white-house-says-2024-04-17/</guid></item><item><title>国际货币基金组织理事会支持对贷款转官方欠款政策进行重大改革</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/imf-board-backs-key-change-lending-into-official-arrears-policy-2024-04-17/</link><description>国际货币基金组织董事会支持一项重大变革，以赋予其更多自由来支持受危机影响的国家，即使与中国等大债权国政府的债务重新谈判仍在进行中。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 11:07:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/imf-board-backs-key-change-lending-into-official-arrears-policy-2024-04-17/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：鲍威尔直言不讳地暗示降息计划将被搁置</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-04-17/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 10:11:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-04-17/</guid></item><item><title>法国、西班牙推出 TikTok Lite 后，欧盟询问 TikTok Lite 对儿童的风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tiktok-quizzed-by-eu-tiktok-lite-launch-france-spain-2024-04-17/</link><description>欧盟委员会周三表示，由于担心 TikTok Lite 对儿童和用户心理健康的潜在影响，字节跳动旗下 TikTok 已被要求在 24 小时内对其本月在法国和西班牙推出的新应用 TikTok Lite 进行风险评估。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 09:52:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/tiktok-quizzed-by-eu-tiktok-lite-launch-france-spain-2024-04-17/</guid></item><item><title>拜登在匹兹堡呼吁对中国金属征收更高关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/biden-call-higher-tariffs-chinese-metals-steel-city-pittsburgh-2024-04-17/</link><description>美国总统乔·拜登周三将呼吁对中国金属产品大幅提高关税，这是旨在取悦摇摆州宾夕法尼亚州钢铁工人的一揽子政策的一部分，但此举可能会激怒北京。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 09:06:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/biden-call-higher-tariffs-chinese-metals-steel-city-pittsburgh-2024-04-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国汽车制造商一汽汽车金融部门推出无首付贷款</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-automaker-faws-auto-finance-unit-launches-loan-with-no-down-payment-2024-04-17/</link><description>中国国有汽车制造商一汽集团的汽车金融部门推出了无首付贷款计划，成为自政府取消最低还款额以来首批采取此举措的供应商之一。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 09:04:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-automaker-faws-auto-finance-unit-launches-loan-with-no-down-payment-2024-04-17/</guid></item><item><title>大众汽车将与小鹏汽车合作推出新架构以降低中国电动汽车成本</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-roll-out-new-architecture-with-xpeng-cut-china-ev-costs-2024-04-17/</link><description>大众汽车公司周三表示，它已经与中国合作伙伴小鹏汽车开发了一种新的智能电动汽车架构，这家德国汽车制造商表示，这将有助于其在其最大的市场上提供更实惠的电动汽车。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 08:47:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-roll-out-new-architecture-with-xpeng-cut-china-ev-costs-2024-04-17/</guid></item><item><title>随着中国担忧加剧，日本公司再次向美国发起进攻</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/japan/japan-inc-makes-renewed-us-push-china-fears-mount-2024-04-17/</link><description>由于对中国需求和北京对供应链影响力的担忧促使日本企业明显转向全球最大经济体，因此越来越多的日本企业将其增长计划转向美国。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 08:14:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/japan/japan-inc-makes-renewed-us-push-china-fears-mount-2024-04-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国田协承诺在半程马拉松惨败后采取行动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/athletics/chinas-federation-promises-action-after-half-marathon-debacle-2024-04-17/</link><description>周日北京半程马拉松的视频显示，三名选手似乎放慢速度，以便让中国选手何洁超越他们并获胜，中国田径协会（CAA）誓言加强对其路跑赛事的监管。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 07:58:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/athletics/chinas-federation-promises-action-after-half-marathon-debacle-2024-04-17/</guid></item></channel></rss>